{"tid":532438,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫我生兒子吧！　男控6旬老闆猥褻","createTime":"2018-01-18T00:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T08:34:21.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46fdcda971160f39dbdd5ac96709bd9b3fe70628","tid":532438,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:17:30.000Z","msg":"男員工阿華（化名）控老闆摸他下體，還傳訊息「你變女生當我老婆，幫我生兒子」，他感到不舒服報警。法院審理發現，阿華的指控多有瑕疵，他說對方傳下體照片給他，生殖器有斑，但實際上沒有，法官一審判老闆無罪，檢方不服上訴仍被駁回。<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，判決書指出，阿華前年10月21日在台中一家五金行工作，他稱洪姓老闆（60歲）用手拍其褲檔、從後方環抱住他，甚至拉下他外褲及內褲說：「你屁股真的很白」。洪否認碰觸對方身體，坦承傳「你變女生當我老婆，幫我生兒子 」的訊息給阿華。<br />\n法院審理時發現，阿華言詞矛盾有瑕疵。二審合議庭法官審酌阿華與老闆有解僱及資遣費計算嫌隙，且阿華年齡、身高、體重等都較優勢，被猥褻當下隱忍，過幾天才理論不合常情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180118/1280831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180118%2F1280831&d=dYnu1y3uyfz1DBULOnZBSbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=14c44188\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180118%2F1280831&h=06d514cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180118/1280831</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8cb7b1cfbdde8568b064d9347ef947902cfb58","tid":532438,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:20:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00306e8efcce2fba9339c28fe13f0b23d16277fe","tid":532438,"uid":41250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:55:10.000Z","msg":"真係台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a160712c017ee1179365002425713fdf6ee58a7","tid":532438,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:57:08.000Z","msg":"咁樣算唔算gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a47190c3d80da0e38719f91ff77bb213bbf7365","tid":532438,"uid":121496,"like":0,"dis